　　日\r\n                               書記官   劉  珀  妤","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c187%2c20220214%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,187,20220214,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"187","JDATE":"20220214","JTITLE":"侮辱"}